Introduction What Tools We Use eslint-plugin-vuejs-accessibility @axe-core/playwright Running Accessibility Tests Skipping Accessibility Tests Locally Skipping Accessibility Tests in CI Accessibility Report Introduction Accessibility is a crucial aspect of web development. It ensures that web applications are usable by everyone, including people with disabilities.
What Tools We Use eslint-plugin-vuejs-accessibility We use eslint-plugin-vuejs-accessibility to quickly catch accessibility issues in the codebase. This plugin is used in the @ownclouders/eslint-config.
@axe-core/playwright We use @axe-core/playwright to automatically test the accessibility of the ownCloud Web client.
